{
  "stem": "18581.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 338.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So at that time, it was already a government which was headed, I believe, by General Cernius.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it had some people from the right and from the left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe-- I'm not so sure, but I believe it was Cernius.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "C-E-R-N-I-U-S.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also, after him was the-- another [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] no.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't-- I don't--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember the other name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I lived, in the beginning, on-- in a hotel on Szopena street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "S-Z-O-P-E-N-A.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stayed there a couple of months until I found, with a friend of mine, an apartment on [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That means [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Valenska ?] Street.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I lived there through the-- all the time until the Germans game.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Economics.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- they didn't have foreign affairs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they had what they called, more or less, politics.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- but of course, this changed when-- after the Russians got hold of Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then-- then, of course, politics became involved with Marxism and Leninism.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, I worked as a-- an-- with a official interpreter of the Lithuanians district court of Vilna.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I translated from Lithuanian-- actually, from Polish and from Russian into Lithuanian.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what I did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After a few months, I landed a job in Vilna, in Vilnius, in a suburb called [NON-ENGLISH]-- I mean, that's where they sent me-- to work in the Lithuanian passport department.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It belonged to the ministry of the interior.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was around [INAUDIBLE] the municipality of Vilnius.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Simply by applying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Simply by applying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was the only Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All my friends were Lithuanian students, boys and-- men and women, who all did the same thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this gave us flexibility, because we worked only till 2 o'clock, I believe, in the afternoon, or till 3:00.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
